Message.Title: If I'm going to be stuck unemployed and as a loser I might as well do it
Message.Msg: If I'm going to be stuck unemployed and as a loser I might as well do it where I grew up so I can enjoy going out and not be looked down on by #$%$ city people. I won't be able to go to therapy anymore or at least until another agency accepts me. Without you guys I could safely say everyone hates me. It's why I am a virgin. People hate me here to the point talking to them makes them very uncomfortable. I can't even talk to them or risk being labeled as a creep. I just have no drive to succeed anymore. Everyone in the city hated me so I'm not sure if things will be any different in the suburbs.
